name: Concave
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
Concave is a community-driven, product and investment organization that aims to bring value to stakers through the development of innovative DeFi products and active treasury management. 

Concave will introduce several novel solutions to grow its treasury while ensuring long-term stakers receive the highest returns.
